== Notes == {{reflist|1|group="note"|refs= <ref name="marshall">[[Marshall Thundering Herd|Marshall]] was a member of the MAC from 1953 to 1969 and again from 1997 to 2004. They left the conference following the [[2004 NCAA Division I-A football season|2004 season]] to become a member of [[Conference USA]].</ref>
<ref name="butler">[[Butler Bulldogs|Butler]] was only a MAC member from 1944 to 1950. They currently play football in the [[Football Championship Subdivision]] of [[NCAA Division I]].</ref>
<ref name="cincinnati">[[Cincinnati Bearcats football|Cincinnati]] left the Mid-American Conference following the [[1953 NCAA Division I-A football season|1953 season]] and is currently a member of the [[Big East]].</ref>
<ref name="central_florida">[[UCF Knights football|Central Florida]] was only a member of the MAC from 2002 to 2005, when they left to become a member of Conference USA, along with Marshall.</ref> }}
